name: Upcoming 10k personal TT pacing test
description: Running a personal 10k TT on October 9th for Dad Strides podcast running weekend. Wanted to see how I could do on this loop going pretty hard hoping to gage how realistically I can hit my goal. It’s 45 minutes/4:30 pace so the chances right now feel less than likely but nonetheless gonna try as hard as I can to get there. Let’s go!
